thread.title: Natalee Townsend
thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Natalee Townsend

author: Natalee Townsend
title: Natalee Townsend
text: My experience at Peaches was great! All the employees really helped me find the prefect quince dress. They were all friendly and we're quick to help. A special thank you to Jocelyn who really helped make my quince dreams come true. She was determined to find my size and made sure everything fit seamlessly. I love my dress and I can't wait to go back for other future events. Peaches was definitely worth the hour and a half drive.
